summary: This mod adds 4 female presets (at the moment) for chargen extension.
descriptionHtml:
[color=yellow]DESCRIPTION[/color]

Basically what the title says, this mod adds 4 female presets to the nord race. Currently it has only 4 but maybe I'll add more if you guys liked it :D

[color=yellow]REQUIRED MODS(to look exactly like the screenies):[/color]

[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal by Hello Santa[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31797/?]Ponytail Hairstyles by Azar[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?/]RaceMenu by Expired[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36925/?/]CharGen Extension by Expired[/url]
download only "core" and "morphs by nuska"

... AND

SG female pack (not on nexus, just google it)

[color=yellow]INSTALLATION[/color]

NMM or extract to data folder

[color=yellow]HOW TO SEE IN-GAME[/color]

type in console 'showracemenu' select nord race. choose from preset slot 0 to 3 and hit load preset.

[color=blue]RECOMMENDED MODS[/color]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]


CREDITS:

expired6978
hellosanta
Azar
